{"parentUuid":"0516777a-1549-4fe8-b11d-928419229459","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01NjSERKuQCHLkLWo38sLWQ5","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"鋭い指摘です。\n\n`List` がレシーバーのフィールドを一切使わないなら、そのメソッドを持つインターフェースは「状態を持つ型」を前提にしすぎている可能性があります。\n\nその場合、インターフェースを関数型に分解する方が適切かもしれません。\n\n```go\n// Before\ntype Lister interface {\n    List(nextCursor string)\n}\n\n// After\ntype ListFunc func(nextCursor string)\n```\n\nただし、**今後レシーバーを使う可能性が明確にある**場合は現状維持も合理的です。\n\n現在の `CoursesService.List` はどんな実装になっていますか？コードを見れば判断しやすいです。"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":214,"cache_read_input_tokens":6921,"output_tokens":220,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":214,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CZLjHyFKNjnikijkSVSco","type":"assistant","uuid":"93ca1f40-4d49-4ceb-9dad-c88a62c86785","timestamp":"2026-03-23T21:34:39.517Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/haru/ghq/github.com/harusame0616/ijuku","sessionId":"33ab2c7d-48be-4dc9-968f-21883ec9780a","version":"2.1.81","gitBranch":"main"}
